Class Burst

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.model.Burst
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Burst
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A bean class that contains the Burst information that appears on the Diagnostics View Chart and the Burst Analysis panel of the Statistics tab.
